    "date": "2026-03-12T14:12:13Z",
    "text": "National Emergency Medical Services Memorial Extension Act\n\nThis bill reauthorizes the National Emergency Medical Services Memorial Foundation to establish\u00a0in Washington, DC, a monument to commemorate the commitment and service represented by emergency medical services. This authorization expires seven years after enactment of the bill."
